/*
 * This Hyperlambda snippet demonstrates how to convert the value of a node from its original type to an integer.
 *
 * 1. [.bar:57]
 *    * Declares a node named [.bar] with a string value of "57".
 *
 * 2. [convert:x:-]
 *    * Converts the value of the node referenced by the expression to an integer.
 *
 * 3. [type:int]
 *    * Specifies that the target type for the conversion is an integer.
 */
.bar:57
convert:x:-
   type:int